[strata] 89678 rows -> /Users/davidoff/DropboxExternal/dataProcessed//bca_vancouver_strata.rds
[duplex] 4132 rows -> /Users/davidoff/DropboxExternal/dataProcessed//bca_vancouver_duplex.rds
> 
